{"tid":2130520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"60多歲保安吳先生自沙士起帶飯露天進食：示威令疫情再爆發","createTime":"2020-07-29T08:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:04:06.000Z","uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4ee4387dab3576e694b39725c3a18b7803eafa","tid":2130520,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116804973_3309329369152660_678847669758445855_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=oW96qjvvjvcAX_2l1o_&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=273178b660c42d4e47fc1138aad47510&amp;oe=5F46AA4B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116804973_3309329369152660_678847669758445855_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DoW96qjvvjvcAX_2l1o_%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D273178b660c42d4e47fc1138aad47510%26oe%3D5F46AA4B&h=844058bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全面禁止堂食今日正式生效，60 多歲保安員吳先生，本來可以在保安室食午餐，但他表示自沙士起已經帶飯到星光大道露天地方食飯，「呢啲嘢（疫情）永遠都係兜兜轉轉。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱讚政府禁止堂食措施正確，對他無任何影響，因為他從不到餐廳吃飯。他又批評集體示威行動令到疫情再次爆發，「政府後尾放鬆，聽啲人話無自由，唔俾示威遊行嗰啲.......唔洗聽人哋㗎，疫情還疫情，我哋唔理政治」。<br />\n<br />\n吳先生一度強調擔心人口密集會成為病毒傳播的溫床，卻認為市民乘搭地鐵上班比起搭巴士、的士更安全，「最安全係搭西鐵，啲火車一到站就消毒，的士巴士空氣唔流通就最危險。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3309329365819327/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3309329365819327%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6aCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=0f30f55b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3309329365819327/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"41b1e9dc8ec0fede6dd52aa02554fcfc82b138e2","tid":2130520,"uid":55458,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:56:56.000Z","msg":"吳先生令到疫情再次爆發"},{"pid":"7661a54387667674874fcb43d4b7d09c4d5403c7","tid":2130520,"uid":30743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"咁你抵撚死"},{"pid":"44b30433a9649fad34d77eacc3e7428dd7483781","tid":2130520,"uid":46906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:57:40.000Z","msg":"dont make on9 famous"},{"pid":"749de151cba33d6798fd69cba6f2a6a4709b1dd5","tid":2130520,"uid":62749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"話左藍屍係on9, 只信港共fake news"},{"pid":"3ea3cf914a86ad50d96ac02b233ff459329840f1","tid":2130520,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"唔係最衰佔中咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c53ec25e31b5174ea408c8ff5f601dc94625e29","tid":2130520,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"????源頭唔係示威喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e309dc112fcedb0a91dff9c7f36c6f47848b05d7","tid":2130520,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"佢呢D真無腦要快d比肺炎手足搞撚掂"},{"pid":"39138ab77de2e1b56680d3eb74b1b1f18040742f","tid":2130520,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb626598fb8f55d7b6887dfc3c8eb88117d22a7","tid":2130520,"uid":15590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"比人逼害都懵然不知<br />\n冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f54248202ddad9ab672f3b4644444764dcea29","tid":2130520,"uid":311904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"最安全係搭西鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> CLS"}]}